==English==

===Pronunciation===
*Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪkɪt|-ɪkɪt]]

===Noun===
'''ticket''' (plural: [[tickets]])

#a [[pass]] entitling the holder to admission to a [[show]], [[concert]], etc.
#a pass entitling the holder to board a train, a plane, or other means of transportation
#a [[citation]] for a traffic violation. <!-- US only? -->
#a permit to operate a machine on a building site. <!-- Australia only? -->

